      "widgets_values": [
        "MV-SAM3D paper reproduction (arXiv:2603.11633).\n\nScene From Dir with empty scene_dir uses the paper's own bundled example scene (vendor/MV-SAM3D/data/example: 8 views of a stuffed toy). Defaults reproduce the published entropy-weighted run: seed 42, stage1 50 / stage2 25 steps, SS entropy layer 9, SLAT entropy layer 6, alpha 30.\n\nFirst run builds the pipeline (~2-3 min), full run ~5 min on a 16 GB RTX 5070 Ti (peak ~14 GB with offload on)."
      ],
      "color": "#432",
      "bgcolor": "#653"
    },
